# Suspiros de Papel — Core Rules

**Business:** Personalized gifts (sublimation, laser engraving, stationery) — Zihuatanejo, México
**Stack:** Next.js 16 (App Router) · React 19 · TypeScript · Tailwind CSS · pnpm
**Phase:** 1 — Landing page only. No backend yet. `src/features/` is RESERVED.

## Package Manager

**PNPM ONLY.** Never write `npm`, never generate `package-lock.json`.

```bash
pnpm dev          # start dev server
pnpm build        # production build
pnpm lint         # eslint
pnpm add <pkg>    # add dependency
```

Run `pnpm lint && pnpm build` before every commit.

## Directory Contract

```
src/app/              → pages + layouts ONLY (no business logic)
src/components/ui/    → stateless primitives: Button, Container
src/components/layout/→ Navbar, Footer
src/components/sections/ → page-level sections (Hero, Portfolio, etc.)
src/constants/        → pure static data (no React, no side effects)
src/hooks/            → custom hooks
src/lib/              → pure utility functions
src/types/            → shared TypeScript types
src/features/         → RESERVED Phase 2 — do not touch
```

Import rules: sections/ may not import other sections/. ui/ may not import sections/ or constants/.

## Exports

**Named exports only.** Default exports are forbidden.

```tsx
export function MySection() { ... }   // ✅
export default function MySection() { ... }  // ❌
```

## Design System

- Colors → CSS vars (`text-primary`, `bg-accent`, `text-secondary`, etc.) — **NEVER hardcode hex**
- Headings → `font-headline` (Noto Serif)
- Body → `font-body` (Plus Jakarta Sans)
- No `style={{}}` inline styles — exception: `objectPosition` on `<Image>` only
- No new Google Fonts without updating `layout.tsx` + `tailwind.config.ts`

## WhatsApp URLs

```ts
import { formatWhatsAppUrl } from "@/lib/whatsapp"
const link = formatWhatsAppUrl("Hola, me interesa un pedido")
```

## Scroll Reveal Pattern

```tsx
const ref = useScrollReveal<HTMLElement>()
<section ref={ref} className="scroll-reveal section-padding">
```

## Forbidden

`npm` · `any` types · `console.log` · `style={{}}` (except objectPosition) · hardcoded hex · default exports · `framer-motion` · business logic in `app/page.tsx` · cross-section imports

## Language

UI copy: Spanish. Code/names/comments: English.
